<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فِيهَا كَسْباً نَادِراً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَكُلُّهَا جَائِزَةٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا ضَمَانَ فِيهَا إِلَّا بِتَعَدٍّ أَوْ تَفْرِيطٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتَصِحُّ المُسَاقَاةُ عَلَى:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> شَجَرٍ لَهُ ثَمَرٌ يُؤْكَلُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَثَمَرَةٍ مَوْجُودَةٍ بِجُزْءٍ مِنْهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَعَلَى شَجَرٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span> يَغْرِسُهُ وَيَعْمَلُ عَلَيْهِ حَتَّى يُثْمِرَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>بِجُزْءٍ مِنَ الثَّمَرَةِ أَوِ الشَّجَرِ أَوْ مِنْهُمَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ فَسَخَ:</span> مَالِكٌ قَبْلَ ظُهُورِ ثَمَرَةٍ: فَلِعَامِلٍ أُجْرَتُهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> أَوْ عَامِلٌ:</span> فَلَا شَيْءَ لَهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتُمْلَكُ الثَّمَرَةُ:</span> بِظُهُورِهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- فَعَلَى عَامِلٍ تَمَامُ عَمَلٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إِذَا فُسِخَتْ بَعْدَهُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (ب): وشجر.<br>(٢) في (د): العمل.</p> </div>